{lang-eng}As I behold You, I’m changed from glory to glory.
As I adore You, my heart falls prostrate before You.
And I cry, “Holy, Holy, Holy, Holy, Holy is my God and King.”{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}As I exalt You, my faith rises up to acknowledge You.
And as I speak to You, I’m ushered into Your presence.
And I cry, “ Holy, Holy, Holy, Holy, Holy is my God and King.”{/lang-eng}
